name: RadaroSDK-iOS
summary: RadaroSDK: Essential Components of the Radaro App.
description:
RadaroSDK is a modular library encapsulating core features of the Radaro application.
It provides a reduced yet robust functionality set of the Radaro app, available on the App Store.
Developers can leverage RadaroSDK to integrate key Radaro features into their applications,
promoting enhanced user experience and advanced functionalities.
